(nil
 "The main bridges that connect the **East Bay** and **West Bay (San Francisco / Peninsula)** are:\n\n- **San Francisco–Oakland Bay Bridge** — connects **San Francisco ↔ Oakland/Yerba Buena Island** (I‑80).\n- **Richmond–San Rafael Bridge** — connects **Richmond ↔ San Rafael (Marin County)** (I‑580).\n- **San Mateo–Hayward Bridge** — connects **San Mateo (Peninsula) ↔ Hayward (East Bay)** (CA‑92).\n- **Dumbarton Bridge** — connects **Menlo Park/East Palo Alto ↔ Fremont/Newark** (CA‑84).\n\nRelated (not East↔West Bay, but often mentioned):\n- **Carquinez Bridge** — connects **Vallejo ↔ Crockett** (I‑80), between Solano and Contra Costa counties.")
